{"tid":1921434,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"鼓勵黃店登記飲食界及進出口界","createTime":"2020-03-12T03:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T06:50:26.000Z","uid":269061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06ec9a45cdbbdea8e1969132e5202926b20b6e5b","tid":1921434,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"鼓勵黃店登記飲食界及進出口界，希望佢地登記後，可以係facebook 宣傳一下。之後大家可以大力懲罰。我知道有d 黃店就黎挨唔住，但都希望把握最後機會用選票屌走廿蚊張。<br />\n<br />\n登記飲食界及進出口界方法<br />\n<br />\n林瑞華：飲食界選民登記仍不理想，希望各食店登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3PP0mi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3PP0mi.jpg&h=548ffc4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有一間成立超過一年嘅公司就可以做到<br />\n你仲唔去申請進出口牌照？<br />\n之後你就可以登記做功能組別進出口界選民。￼<br />\n<br />\n#功能組別 #登記￼￼ #條肥佬連續四屆自動當選<br />\n<br />\n電子證書申請表：<a href=\"https://www.ecert.gov.hk/product/ecert/apply/img/e-Cert_(S_O_E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecert.gov.hk%2Fproduct%2Fecert%2Fapply%2Fimg%2Fe-Cert_%28S_O_E&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=eaa78985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ecert.gov.hk/product/ecert/apply/img/e-Cert_(S_O_E</a>)_N.pdf"},{"pid":"c7166af7243bb0980e4c36bf3d3a8bb6f4b66394","tid":1921434,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"例子：<br />\n慈雲山嵐屋Arashi<br />\n<br />\n致好心人們：<br />\n<br />\n老細係上年6月已經登記左飲食界功能界別選民。<br />\n<br />\n到目前為止仍然有效。<br />\n<br />\n#齊心創造歷史時刻。"},{"pid":"47578f8b6c29493fd2a65be4ddffcef265fbbe9c","tid":1921434,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T03:58:05.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以copy 登記方法，用各途徑向黃店老闆宣傳登記"},{"pid":"5d1b1c9d566c7dcb186ee2e1d5fc4ff8cf5c50a6","tid":1921434,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:38:21.000Z","msg":"用心制作，請用5 分鐘了解功能組別登記<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p59mZyffEao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp59mZyffEao&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=2bfeb5d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p59mZyffEao</a>"},{"pid":"64acc1c5d6e3d9aa7bbec19479bc25e443d6e6de","tid":1921434,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:21:31.000Z","msg":"【飲食界嘅黃店都有懶人選民登記生成器】<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山各自努力，代手足轉發：<br />\n<br />\n用手機相機scan個QR code，填好上面嘅表格，神奇嘅事就會發生：一份填好晒資料嘅表格，係幾日之內寄到上門，或者有義工親自送上門，你簽上大名就大功告成！<br />\nClick以下連結，可用到「飲食界選民生成器」。<br />\n「個人持牌」版：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/KTzMvtPeyeh4cpZ46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FKTzMvtPeyeh4cpZ46&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=65364325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/KTzMvtPeyeh4cpZ46</a><br />\n「公司持牌」版：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/EA7e4aRUPAVXArKi9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FEA7e4aRUPAVXArKi9&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=84704c56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/EA7e4aRUPAVXArKi9</a><br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明，歡迎搵我地！<br />\nwhatsapp: 9180 3949<br />\ntelegram: RicePigLin<br />\nemail: ricepiglin@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n轉載請註明出處及歡迎手足投稿：民間清算師專頁<br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vendettists\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvendettists&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=2a061567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vendettists</a><br />\nTG：<a href=\"https://t.me/revengehi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevengehi&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=6afd024e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revengehi</a><br />\n<br />\n#專業清算 #民間清算 #黃店 #懶人包 #飲食界 #登記成選民"},{"pid":"0968308c51a2aa842c26bc67375256e39d7cace2","tid":1921434,"ui